info: Rating, 1 star,  · August 2023,  · Stayed over a week
rating_comment:
I have stayed at nearly 100 Airbnb locations, but my experience at this Airbnb was particularly troubling. Despite positive initial impressions from photos, my experience was marked by numerous issues:
Strike 1: Visa complications & a refusal to provide required contact info started my stay on the wrong foot. The absence of working desk as in the photos led to discomfort, while cleanliness & pest control were inadequate.
Strike 2: Persistent noise from construction & broadcasted prayers disrupted my work & sleep. The internet & power outages further hindered my work. An urgent need for assistance w receiving a shipment was met w obstruction and additional costs.
Strike 3: Upon checkout, I was blindsided by a $350 charge for a non-functional TV that I hadn't even used. My attempt to resolve the issue was met w a baseless accusation of dishonesty from management.
Overall, my experience was marked by consistent problems, unmet expectations, & hostile customer service Renters Beware

-The hotel is in a residential area. There is nothing much around it. When we booked it showed it’s location in the city center but in fact it’s 17 km from the center. We wanted to cancel the rest of the booking but the management wasn’t cooperative. Dispute was settled by Airbnb.
